      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test sul massimo                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su tipo debitore                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-sdb-tip-dbt       not  = 01
                     go to stp-srt-inp-sdb-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su codice cliente                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-sdb-cod-dbt       not  = rf-mgr-cod-arc
                     go to stp-srt-inp-sdb-900.
       stp-srt-inp-sdb-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Selezioni su [sdb]                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
